{"tid":180993,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【DSE】好撚驚呀 聽日考","createTime":"2017-03-31T09:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T10:50:31.000Z","uid":10140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1428aa20d4784e6a96f5f6d5c8cd2fc9495bc8fd","tid":180993,"uid":10140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T09:47:41.000Z","msg":"想問有經驗巴絲一般早幾多到考場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n試場係咪一定好似平時學校考試咁 有勁大個mon顯示倒計時你睇 定乜都冇 自己帶錶<br />\n<br />\n同埋最尾十五分鐘同五分鐘係咪一定會提你架 定睇心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68debd92872fcf17cf6a6043f201ab181850b752","tid":180993,"uid":96983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T09:59:34.000Z","msg":"會提,有鐘,早半個鐘到"},{"pid":"eccf32fdc8c00450780cbbb5c0daab6b6d3923d8","tid":180993,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:03:11.000Z","msg":"早一晚"},{"pid":"edfe9cdea5476cd2dbd366f53d9fa2b243d76693","tid":180993,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:19:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問有經驗巴絲一般早幾多到考場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n試場係咪一定好似平時學校考試咁 有勁大個mon顯示倒計時你睇 定乜都冇 自己帶錶<br />\n<br />\n同埋最尾十五分鐘同五分鐘係咪一定會提你架 定睇心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n建議自己帶鐘，即使個地方有未必可以啱你角度"},{"pid":"a5e6c4aa22a962fa794de44b76a37a55b3cee44e","tid":180993,"uid":350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:34:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> feel到巴打真係好緊張"},{"pid":"434848d1e67d09676b3ea7bfad8af3db9a4e4f48","tid":180993,"uid":350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:35:43.000Z","msg":"最好帶住隻錶啦點都 方便自己<br />\n同埋都真係有機會現場個鐘好虧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d229ae15b68a4361e91efa241cb7e9a17c5dcc","tid":180993,"uid":350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:36:37.000Z","msg":"如果有鼻感敏既巴絲記得帶備大量既紙巾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a232c9ad2103cf32c894325684fded3a14b20e48","tid":180993,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:38:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9417941c2a97c98d14b4eb572bfabc347bdd2e32","tid":180993,"uid":73064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:39:01.000Z","msg":"驚西咩⋯⋯到你出黎做野就知咩叫驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：老屎忽"},{"pid":"c9c7f8f3cbb2693e236a593be4de56042716d3e9","tid":180993,"uid":3230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:40:45.000Z","msg":"上年會早個半鐘去到<br />\n淡定啲今晚早啲訓啦"},{"pid":"bf408c221d787c367c6ad08b2991f5cd3128e256","tid":180993,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:42:49.000Z","msg":"聽日有野考咩"},{"pid":"bfff9060aed465dd044b3c53610ddc787a2087e0","tid":180993,"uid":4596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:43:58.000Z","msg":"早太多遲太多又唔好所以早半個鐘就差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打唔好咁緊張 我舊年都係溫曬書勁有信心咁入去考 結果考嗰陣時好輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然出到嚟成績未如理想不過點都話有三大讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:非CU engine<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9293e29cef268ed959ddccb920a4750594ff20","tid":180993,"uid":32149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:45:59.000Z","msg":"上年早1個鐘到，考緊你唔會咁得閒抬頭望鐘，最好擺隻錶/細鐘喺枱頭方便自己，有提示<br />\nbtw考其實冇嘢驚，係驚都係驚放榜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa1f69ab0cf985ec819bd3fddcee551d069a9f9a","tid":180993,"uid":10140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:47:13.000Z","msg":"多謝各位巴絲提醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f993a9d4e7e2e49f1cb0aac1545cc584121dc631","tid":180993,"uid":10348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:50:25.000Z","msg":"如果考之前&quot;溫哂&quot; 咁考前有咩做<br />\n有d想打機但覺得會搞到心散"},{"pid":"d6de581a6d81cec297d9afc8155f230ed8a315c5","tid":180993,"uid":21664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:50:31.000Z","msg":"早一個到啦.鐘望下googlemap考場點去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽日考之前就唔洗溫啦放鬆下個人. 加油<br />\n<br />\n16DSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}